{"title":"湘江腊月（外一首）","authors":["未央"],"dates":[{"year":1961,"month":2,"day":2}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"湘江腊月（外一首）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"未央"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"腊月的湘江分外繁忙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大船小舟不断线地来往，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白天像闹市车水马龙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夜晚像银河撒着星光。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"汽轮唱着高腔飞驰，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"帆船搧着白翅翱翔，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长长的拖船是水上列车，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"巧妙的“八面风”能走八方。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这里满载南特良种，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那里装着永兴红薯王，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这里堆满农用石灰，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那里叠着扁担箩筐。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"东边运走杀虫药粉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"西边送去壮苗乳浆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"各式水泵叫人眼花缭乱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刚出厂的“东方红”闪着红光。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"腊月的湘江分外繁忙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"车水马龙掀起滚滚白浪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当大军正在养兵歇马，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"号角已经先在这里吹响！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"编蓑衣，织斗笠"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妹子在编蓑衣，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妹子在织斗笠，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风雪的冬天就要溜走，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"快快迎接明媚的春季。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两手不停编棕丝，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好似阳雀花间飞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十指轻轻织竹篾，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好似蜻蜓来点水。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"编啊！织啊！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妹子心里甜如蜜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"早早催得春来到，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春雨中哥妹比高低。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"脱掉笨重的棉袄，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"露出壮实的手臂。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"身披崭新的蓑衣，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"头戴美丽的斗笠。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这边田里妹插秧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那边田里哥扶犁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"任它雨点像湘江水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一对山鹰并翅儿飞。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}